<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/10110896-robert-blumenthal"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1339293952i/10110896.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/10110896-robert-blumenthal">Robert Blumenthal</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">It is more like a child using her imagination in an deeply challenging life situation. There is somewhat of a fairy tale element to parts of the story<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">It is more like a child using her imagination in an deeply challenging life situation. There is somewhat of a fairy tale element to parts of the story, but no ghosts or spiritual presences at all. It is a truly wonderful book.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
